' RAWPOWER
' WHAT DOES THIS DO?
' does the following:
' 1. runs TabandDupe, which replaces spaces with tabs and makes a duplicate of a line of Hul'q'umi'num' text, then 2. StraightDupe, which places a top line and transliterates from Straight to Orthography, then 3. FourLinePrep, which puts another extra line in, then finally 4. runs the autoglosser on the bottom (non-English) line to hopefully replace all the grammatical morphemes with ones to be automatically glossed. As well, it puts each line in its own Word style to make it easier to do something (like pull out all of the lines of just phonetics, or glosses, or what have you.)
' thus the final product should look like this:
'
'   Practical Orthography [style: Orthography]
'   Phonetics [SOURCE] [style: Phonetics]
'   Phonetics with hyphens [style: Phonetics-Hyphen]
'   Gloss [style: Gloss]
'   Translation [style: any, Normal, etc.]
'
'




